lead_paragraph: Federal income tax returns from 2007 through 2014 for Hillary Rodham Clinton and her husband, former President Bill Clinton, show a surge in earnings in recent years and provide new details on aspects of their business dealings.

headline.main: A Look at Hillary Clinton's 2007-2014 Federal Tax Returns
